Application.Description: The CRM application includes all the core functionality required of a basic customer relationship management system by providing a central place for all of your sales, marketing, and support representatives to access and manage customer Accounts, Contacts, Leads, Cases and Opportunities. Also included in the CRM application is a Leads portal which you can embed into your website to accept lead submissions from visitors to your website. Configure as many different leads portals and pages as you want to manage all of your marketing campaigns. Lead records can easily be converted into Account records as needed by using standard conversion mapping functionality. Feel free to add your own Case portal to allow web submission of Cases. As with any other Progress Rollbase application, CRM can be fully customized and extended to meet the needs of your organization. For example, administrators can create custom workflow events to assign incoming Leads to specific users based on territory assignments.

Lang.text: Also included in the CRM application is a Leads portal which you can embed into your website to accept lead submissions from prospects. Configure as many different leads portals and pages as you want to manage all of your marketing campaigns. Lead records can easily be converted into Account records as needed by using standard conversion mapping functionality. Feel free to build your own Case portal to accept incoming customer support requests.

As a Progress Rollbase administrator you can install any application from the Application Directory with a single click and immediately deploy it to the right people in your organization. All Progress Rollbase applications in the Application Directory are built by other experienced Progress Rollbase users and can be fully customized to meet your needs once installed.

As with any other Progress Rollbase application, CRM can be fully customized and extended to meet the needs of your organization. In addition, once installed this application will automatically be integrated with all of your other Progress Rollbase applications.
If you have questions or comments about this application you can connect with other users via the Progress Rollbase online forum.

The CRM application includes all the core functionality required of a basic customer relationship management system by providing a central place for all of your sales, marketing, and support representatives to access and manage customer Accounts, Contacts, Leads, Cases and Opportunities.
The Progress Rollbase Application Directory is a continually growing online exchange where users can browse, test drive, and install web-based business applications on-demand.

This Progress Rollbase application includes a pre-configured set of fields, views, pages, and templates that make it an easier and faster alternative to traditional back-office CRM systems. As a Progress Rollbase Administrator you can completely customize and expand this application to suit your specific business needs. Because this is a Progress Rollbase application it is automatically integrated with all of your other installed Progress Rollbase applications and it can be shared among any of your users.
